title: Led Zeppelin - 1973.05.16 Houston, Texas
description:
Led Zeppelin - 1973.05.16 Houston, Texas   

Led Zeppelin
May 16, 1973
Sam Houston Arena
Houston, Texas
Source: SBD

Source: 
Incomplete excellent soundboard recording. 60 minutes.

Details: 
The recording is a very good balanced professional board tape.

Tracklist:

1. Stairway To Heaven
2. Moby Dick
3. Heartbreaker
4. Whole Lotta Love
5. Communication Breakdown

Total Time: 60:19

Comments:
One word describes this show...violent! The band's playing and 
attack is relentlessly aggressive ...they are pushing everything 
to the limit. This is a great show; Robert really pushes himself 
to the max with the rest of the band
